<subSubSection pageId="117" pageNumber="118" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="117.[151,1437,1075,1749]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">
This genus was established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Hanson, P. &amp; Medina, C. A. &amp; Torres, M. &amp; Melika, G." box="[484,783,1075,1101]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" pagination="75 - 104" refId="ref68899" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Hanson, P., Medina, C. A., Torres, M. &amp; Melika, G. (2012 a) A new genus of oak gallwasps, Zapatella Pujade- Villar &amp; Melika, gen. n., with a description of two new species from the Neotropics (Hymenoptera, Cynipidae, Cynipini). ZooKeys, 210, 75 - 104. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 210.3014." type="journal article" year="2012">
Pujade-Villar 
<emphasis box="[638,684,1075,1101]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">et al</emphasis>
. (2012a)
</bibRefCitation>
as an initial step in reorganising the taxonomy of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">
<taxonomicName authorityName="sensu Burks" authorityYear="1979" box="[1317,1436,1075,1101]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Callirhytis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" sensu="lato">Callirhytis</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[151,265,1111,1137]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" sensu="lato">sensu lato</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
in the Nearctic. It was first described from two Neotropical species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Pujade-Villar &amp; Melika, 2012" authorityName="Pujade-Villar &amp; Melika" authorityYear="2012" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grahami">
<emphasis box="[1041,1251,1111,1137]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Zapatella grahami</emphasis>
Pujade-Villar &amp; Melika, 2012
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Melika &amp; Pujade-Villar, 2012" authorityName="Melika &amp; Pujade-Villar" authorityYear="2012" box="[361,891,1147,1173]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nievesaldreyi">
<emphasis box="[361,540,1147,1173]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. nievesaldreyi</emphasis>
Melika &amp; Pujade-Villar, 2012
</taxonomicName>
, with a further five Nearctic species transferred from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sensu Burks" authorityYear="1979" box="[214,333,1183,1209]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Callirhytis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[214,333,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Callirhytis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName authority="(Weld, 1922)" baseAuthorityName="Weld" baseAuthorityYear="1922" box="[350,632,1183,1209]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cryptica">
<emphasis box="[350,473,1184,1209]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. cryptica</emphasis>
(Weld, 1922)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Weld, 1926)" baseAuthorityName="Weld" baseAuthorityYear="1926" box="[645,926,1183,1210]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="herberti">
<emphasis box="[645,767,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. herberti</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Weld, L. H." box="[783,919,1183,1210]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" pagination="1 - 131" refId="ref70470" refString="Weld, L. H. (1926) Field Notes on Gall-inhabiting Cynipid Wasps with descriptions of new species. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 68 (10), 1 - 131." type="journal article" year="1926">Weld, 1926</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Weld, 1952)" baseAuthorityName="Weld" baseAuthorityYear="1952" box="[939,1202,1183,1210]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="oblata">
<emphasis box="[939,1043,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. oblata</emphasis>
(Weld, 1952)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Ashmead, 1885)" baseAuthorityName="Ashmead" baseAuthorityYear="1885" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quercusmedullae">
<emphasis box="[1215,1436,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. quercusmedullae</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Ashmead, W. H." box="[159,339,1219,1246]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" pagination="5 - 9" refId="ref63405" refString="Ashmead, W. H. (1885) On the cynipidous galls of Florida with descriptions of new species. Transaction of the American Entomological Society, 12, 5 - 9." type="journal article" year="1885">Ashmead, 1885</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Osten Sacken, 1861) (Pujade-Villar et al. 2012 a)" authorityName="Pujade-Villar et al." authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="Osten Sacken" baseAuthorityYear="1861" box="[405,1180,1219,1246]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quercusphellos">
<emphasis box="[405,605,1219,1245]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z. quercusphellos</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Osten Sacken, C. R. von" box="[620,849,1219,1246]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" pagination="47 - 72" refId="ref67812" refString="Osten Sacken, C. R. von (1861) On the Cynipidae of the North American oaks and their galls. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Philadelphia, 1 (1861 - 3), 47 - 72." type="journal article" year="1861">Osten Sacken, 1861</bibRefCitation>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Hanson, P. &amp; Medina, C. A. &amp; Torres, M. &amp; Melika, G." box="[873,1173,1219,1245]" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" pagination="75 - 104" refId="ref68899" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Hanson, P., Medina, C. A., Torres, M. &amp; Melika, G. (2012 a) A new genus of oak gallwasps, Zapatella Pujade- Villar &amp; Melika, gen. n., with a description of two new species from the Neotropics (Hymenoptera, Cynipidae, Cynipini). ZooKeys, 210, 75 - 104. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 210.3014." type="journal article" year="2012">
Pujade-Villar 
<emphasis box="[1033,1084,1219,1245]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">et al</emphasis>
. 2012a
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Since then, five more species have been described from 
<collectingCountry box="[534,649,1255,1281]" name="Colombia" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Colombia</collectingCountry>
: 
<taxonomicName authority="Pujade-Villar &amp; Rodriguez, 2015" authorityName="Pujade-Villar &amp; Rodriguez" authorityYear="2015" box="[659,1143,1255,1282]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Zapatella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="117" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inflata">
<emphasis box="[659,675,1256,1281]" italics="true" pageId="117" pageNumber="118">Z</emphasis>
